title: The Cnidarians
text:
This is the website for the 1st edition of The Cnidarians. This book is currently being written… in the open. The information presented here is a work in progress and should be taken as such. This is likely to be quite the adventure, and I welcome you to follow along over the coming months, years or however long it takes me to write this…



Photograph by Ganapathy Kumar
